38 class basic_stringstream;

98class _LIBCPP_TYPE_VIS ios_base;

100template<class _CharT> struct _LIBCPP_TYPE_VIS_ONLY char_traits;
101template<class _Tp> class _LIBCPP_TYPE_VIS_ONLY allocator;
102
103template <class _CharT, class _Traits = char_traits<_CharT> >
104 class _LIBCPP_TYPE_VIS_ONLY basic_ios;
105
106template <class _CharT, class _Traits = char_traits<_CharT> >
107 class _LIBCPP_TYPE_VIS_ONLY basic_streambuf;
